daily_fact: Despite the closure of Antique Garage Tribeca, the community continues to thrive, showcasing resilience and adaptability in the face of change, as local businesses innovate to meet evolving needs.
topline_md: This weekend, NYC, NJ, and CT are bracing for a winter storm, while traffic disruptions are reported on the George Washington Bridge and a deadly crash raises concerns about sanitation operations. Additionally, Mayor Mamdani proposes cuts to library funding and plans to close the last emergency migrant shelter by year-end.
